Subject: [PATCH] Fix critical security issues from audit
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Verify Stripe webhook signatures in /api/webhooks/stripe
  (constructEvent with STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET, 400 on mismatch)
- Replace hardcoded admin email gate with profiles.is_admin column
  + shared requireAdmin helper; existing emails seeded via migration 013
- Drop dead ADMIN_EMAILS list in /api/agent
- Add /api/admin/me for client-side admin gate; pass is_admin from
  server layout into AppShellClient instead of email comparison
- Fix createServerClient export alias so consumers compile
- Restore JSX comment in ResultBlock and rename useTeamRole.ts to .tsx
  (both surfaced after removing build-error suppression)

next.config.js still has ignoreBuildErrors/ignoreDuringBuilds set with
a TODO — there are ~38 unrelated pre-existing TS errors that need a
separate cleanup pass before the flags can be removed.
